{"tid":2265362,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[TSLA] 特斯拉文件透露下一座超級工廠不在亞洲","createTime":"2020-10-31T11:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T13:31:56.000Z","uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5bd09931cbe14278974fc1efea66f231dc7fc5","tid":2265362,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"日前馬斯克已經證實特斯拉將在 2021 年進軍印度，再加上他更早前還提過亞洲會有新的超級工廠，而且地點不會在中國，因此外界紛紛猜測特斯拉的下一座超級工廠，坐落點可能會在印度。<br />\n<br />\n但特斯拉日前呈交給美國證券交易委員會的文件，當中卻透露特斯拉下一座超級工廠還是會在美國。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國證券交易委員會的規定，上市公司每一季都要提交被稱為 10-Q 的季度報告，而特斯拉在先前提交的第三季 10-Q 報告當中，列出了當前旗下所有超級工廠的運作和現況。<br />\n<br />\n重點在於，除了加州弗里蒙特、中國上海、德國柏林與美國德州超級工廠之外，特斯拉還列出了一個當前尚未公布的超級工廠，並確認廠址設置在美國，而不是外界預期的印度或亞洲任何國家。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉也在 10-Q 報告當中，確認這座詳細建設定點尚未公告的超級工廠，來將用來主力生產 Roadster 2 電動超跑和 Semi 電動卡車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://autos.yahoo.com.tw/news/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2%E4%B8%8B-%E5%BA%A7%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2-%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%A0%E5%B0%87%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2-roadster-2-074921845.html?fbclid=IwAR2ota1TXp8_0BPWgOAjFbp8RvamonGW_oBNELtmECST_4Xx-KXBPCu0xR0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fautos.yahoo.com.tw%2Fnews%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%259C%25B2%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2-roadster-2-074921845.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ota1TXp8_0BPWgOAjFbp8RvamonGW_oBNELtmECST_4Xx-KXBPCu0xR0&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=31505dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://autos.yahoo.com.tw/news/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2%E4%B8%8B-%E5%BA%A7%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2-%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%A0%E5%B0%87%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2-roadster-2-074921845.html?fbclid=IwAR2ota1TXp8_0BPWgOAjFbp8RvamonGW_oBNELtmECST_4Xx-KXBPCu0xR0</a>"},{"pid":"ae890a5253ac450c29249397680931fcc5d2e0c4","tid":2265362,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZQQKE1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZQQKE1.gif&h=39e1b4d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1e3c9a233185644771a3521aa5f8f52014ffdd","tid":2265362,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"火星超級工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />7000不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f177ae0e3f19cb39e95e4ab4027f0e42e3c15f64","tid":2265362,"uid":323740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2R06Xs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2R06Xs.jpg&h=98bff2d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d99f6be8ec7142df7e220b4c01b9378adabaf63f","tid":2265362,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"咪又係跌 屌你老母"},{"pid":"e88f204e53ab86b649eb9b197504ff610c57fedd","tid":2265362,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d99f6be8ec7142df7e220b4c01b9378adabaf63f","tid":2265362,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"咪又係跌 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回調啫"},{"pid":"9050abce5cc62060ca2b2e8178135d9eb8d374a9","tid":2265362,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1e3c9a233185644771a3521aa5f8f